---
title: Haloumi & Dukkah Couscous Bowl with Sweet Roasted Veggies & Lemon Yoghurt Drizzle
description: Taste the rainbow for dinner tonight with an assortment of colourful roasted veggies and a scattering of sweet currants, all stirred through fluffy, filling couscous. Topped off with golden haloumi and a bite of dukkah, this robust bowl packs a punch in all the right ways.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5e69ac87be4e4a1e5205e94e-0d97dba9.jpg
